Specific code adapted from godot-mcp (per-file headers cite the source
file + line range):

  bridge/tool_utils.gd
    safe_instantiate_class() and supporting class_name resolver
    Source: src/scripts/godot_operations.gd lines ~95-162
    Purpose: instantiate any class — built-in (ClassDB) or user-declared
             via `class_name` — from agent input, with strict regex
             validation.

  tools/implementations/uid/get_uid.gd
  tools/implementations/uid/update_project_uids.gd
    Godot 4.4+ resource-UID handling.
    Source: src/scripts/godot_operations.gd lines ~889-1090
    Purpose: read/regenerate the .uid sidecars that Godot 4.4+ uses to
             track resource references across renames and moves. Edge
             cases for the resave-after-uid-change flow are pre-debugged
             upstream (godot-mcp issues #102, #104).

